WHY
This is a big one. Because the foundation of web3 is empowering creators, collectors, builders - EVERYONE to own their assets. Myth Division is building its foundation on empowering YOU to be a part of the MD universe. You get to build and add to the story and brand.

Sandbox, unreal engine 5, 3D avatars fully rigged for anything your favorite hyped project thinks it is ready for, your local comic ship, your favorite streaming platform, it's all either already here, or on its way.

Comics, animation, movies, video games, world building, storytelling, character creation, eyeball melting fun, creator empowerment.
